articles.summary: The Wall Street Journal: The Vyšší Brod Altar: Christ’s Life in Brilliant Color. This richly illustrated nine-panel work in Prague’s Agnes Cloister emphasizes the humanity in the essential chapters of Christian faith, creating images with universal appeal.

articles.mainIdea: Gilead Sciences to acquire Repare’s RP-3467
